6. Document generation
For 201, NTE, and NOD, use the same document engine.
Flow:
Template
→ Merge employee/case data
→ Generate PDF
→ Save to employee 201 file
→ Send notification
→ Track acknowledgment
Templates needed:
NTE Template
NOD Template
COE Template
Clearance Template
Final Pay Release Template
Warning Letter Template
7. Important rule
Every NTE and NOD must automatically be saved inside:
Employee Profile → 201 File → Disciplinary Records

